{"tid":2343814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"違起底禁令轉載西灣河開真槍警員及家屬資料 網民遭高等法院判監21日","createTime":"2020-12-28T08:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T14:44:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"8b672d770096096789db5e5472380bc17e21870b","tid":2343814,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"高等法院去年頒下防「起底」禁制令，阻止為滋擾目的而披露警務人員個人資料，今日再有違反禁制令個案在高等法院聆訊。去年11月11日早上有警員在西灣河開槍，27歲網民不久後在facebook連續轉載4個帖文，含有警員相片，警員和妻女的個人資料，帖文附有「開真槍呀？有排同你玩，香港警察」、「西灣河殺人犯」、「善惡到頭終有報」等字句。網民承認觸犯禁制令，法官高浩文認為緩刑不足以反映罪責，判處網民入獄21日，是首度有人因觸違反此禁制令已被判即時入獄。<br />\n<br />\n被告是第三個因違反警察起底禁制令而被判刑的人。前兩宗個案分別是設計師在周梓樂墮樓事件後轉載一名警員及家人個人資料，附加「血債血償」和「黑警」等字，以及區議員鄭麗琼轉載涉射盲印尼女記者的警員的資料，評論「請自首！以眼還眼」，兩人均被判囚28日，但獲緩刑1年，毋須入獄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/JA5KGZXAYNANNMHKR2QWK4SNII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FJA5KGZXAYNANNMHKR2QWK4SNII%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=0c72a62f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FJA5KGZXAYNANNMHKR2QWK4SNII%2F&h=277e2de0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/JA5KGZXAYNANNMHKR2QWK4SNII/</a>"},{"pid":"efca79c07d3cca025b143288b3b6088ef5c5e10e","tid":2343814,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b393e96e04514423f0b9c12b9a5544542a9967a","tid":2343814,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d619b8b0d4c4fb12ce236742f288d35e919c6e68","t