lass=\"red\">西灣河殺人犯關家榮</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fa1a7697206b3bbbe8809ef243a1681a4848e0","tid":2343814,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"130fa227e1c1b2680dac25668802fd015fe181d3","tid":2343814,"uid":34789,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:25:11.000Z","msg":"出地球post？定朋友出賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"地球post <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n26.  After the shooting incident on the morning of 11 November 2019, the Defendant saw on his Telegram chats a lot of messages in the Dadfindboy channel, and &ldquo;out of curiosity&rdquo; decided to click into it and scrolled through the messages showing the personal data of PW1 posted by other people.  He says that &ldquo;without a second thought&rdquo; at around 8:48am he reposted a photograph of PW1 and made the personal comment &ldquo;開真槍丫嘛? 有排同你玩香港警察 Hong Kong Police&rdquo; (English translation: &ldquo;Firing a real gun, eh?  Will take time playing with you, the Hong Kong Police, Hong Kong police&rdquo;) on his own Facebook page.  He did so purely because he was so upset and overwhelmed by anger at that time.  He says in his affirmation that he did not intend to incite any violence against PW1.<br />\n<br />\n27.  Subsequently, at 9:06am, 9:25am and 10:25am, the Defendant shared three posts copied from the channel onto his own Facebook page.  The captions were simply copied from the posts.  Again, he says, he was overwhelmed by anger at that time and without pausing to think copied the posts and re-posted them on his own Facebook page.<br />\n<br />\n28.  The Defendant also says that when he made the Facebook Posts, the Doxxing Injunction &ldquo;was not in the forefront&rdquo; of his mind. He did not put the acts together, but had he thought hard and calm enough to realise that his act would amount to a breach of the Doxxing Injunction, he certainly would not have done it.  The Defendant says he has the utmost respect for the Courts of Hong Kong, and would not dream of deliberately breaching an order of the Court.<br />\n<br />\n29.  <strong><span class=\"red\">The Defendant also says that he did not realise the posts on his Facebook page were open to the public.</span></strong>  Rather, he always thought his Facebook Posts were only accessible to his personal Facebook friends, at the time numbering around 600 (around 400 of whom were friends from Thailand, or clients, or people in the same business as him).  So, he says, he did not intend to share his posts publicly to the public at large.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132632&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D132632%26currpage%3DT&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=f551ef12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132632&amp;currpage=T</a>"},{"pid":"7d5ac9803bc819b4cb86d21c09aa3f198289b738","tid":2343814,"uid":188805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"好奇一問, 係咪<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">關家榮</span></span>?"},{"pid":"c009b8954b121c77bec6b449a993384ed58348df","tid":2343814,"uid":263200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d5ac9803bc819b4cb86d21c09aa3f198289b738","tid":2343814,"uid":188805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"好奇一問, 係咪<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">關家榮</span></span>?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"唔準再提<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"maroon\">關家榮</span></span>同埋2隻走失左嘅狗女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0e8c220af1e569a6364c6cbd908cf1bdd22112","tid":2343814,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3a8c4cecef76bba519d386349965cb361d913c","tid":2343814,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"陳又於其中一個貼文加入自己的評論，即「開真槍呀，有排同你玩，香港警察」，陳被控民事藐視法庭罪，他今承認責任，法官高浩文判處緩刑並不適合，最終判處陳即時入獄 21 天，另須支付 2 萬元訟費，為首宗違反警員「起底」禁制令而遭即時判囚的案件。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%A6%81%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E6%A1%88%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84-27-%E6%AD%B2%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%BB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-21-%E6%97%A5%E5%85%BC%E4%BB%98%E5%85%A9%E8%90%AC%E8%A8%9F%E8%B2%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584-27-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25BA%2597%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-21-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25BC%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25A8%259F%25E8%25B